Package: fireR
Title: Download and Load MTBS (Monitoring Trends in Burn Severity) Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Noah", "Weidig", email = "noah.weidig@ufl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides fast, convenient access to MTBS fire perimeter data from
    the USGS. Downloads the composite burned-area extent shapefile, unzips it,
    and returns it as either an 'sf' or 'terra' SpatVector object. Optionally
    filters results to a user-supplied range of fire years.
